can_wear_or_remove

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
can_wear_or_remove -  This method returns whether or not a player can wear or remove a given item.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string can_wear_or_remove(object thing,
object player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the item to be worn or removed.
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the person doing the wearing or removing.
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 for success, a string for failure.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/clothing_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns whether or not a player can wear or remove a given item.
.EP

